{
  "id": "adv_group_moon_04_02",
  "title": "月のテンペスト 04 02",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、その頃の琴乃ちゃんは\nクラスでいじめられていたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So Kotono-chan was being bullied\nin her class back then?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.4254423141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "それほど大袈裟なことじゃないわ\nちょっとクラスで孤立していただけで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It wasn't that big of a deal.\nI was just a bit isolated in class…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6187754948,
      "endTime": 12.247913297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "渚がいつもそばにいてくれたから、どうでもいい\n人達に無視されてもちっとも苦じゃなかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa was always by my side‚ so it didn't matter\nif those insignificant people ignored me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4545797348,
      "endTime": 19.3182303428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5315636952,
      "endTime": 21.4959626038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "むしろ、二年生に進級してからの方が大変だったかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ it was probably tougher after we moved up to our second year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7092959324,
      "endTime": 26.43419408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "二年生になって何があったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What happened in your second year?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6408606131,
      "endTime": 29.7937630255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんの人気が更に上がっていって\nみんなが妹の琴乃ちゃんと仲良くなろうとしたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana-san's popularity increased even more‚\nand everyone wanted to be friends with Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9804295778,
      "endTime": 37.6070735216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "私をいじめてた子が、懲りずにお姉ちゃんのサインを\nもらえないかって頼みに来た時はさすがに呆れたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The girl who bullied me even had the nerve to come and ask for my sister's autograph.\nIt was ridiculous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.800406893,
      "endTime": 45.8505203802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃の琴乃ちゃんは\n麻奈さんとの関係がぎくしゃくしてたしね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan's relationship with Mana-san\nwasn't very good at that time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.0638537327,
      "endTime": 51.4903161923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "どんどん仕事が忙しくなって、一緒にいられる時間が\n減って……それが原因でよく喧嘩するようになって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Work got busier and busier‚ and we had less time to spend together…\nWe started fighting a lot because of that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.683649373,
      "endTime": 61.720248341499996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "渚にはいつも愚痴ばかり言ってた気がするわ\nあの時は迷惑をかけたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel like I was always complaining to Nagisa.\nI'm sorry for burdening you back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.9269148747,
      "endTime": 68.4550833622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "全然迷惑じゃないよ。むしろ、琴乃ちゃんが私にだけ\n弱い一面を見せてくれるのが嬉しかったくらいだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It wasn't a burden at all. In fact‚ I was happy that you showed me your vulnerable side‚\nKotono-chan‚ just to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.6417500097,
      "endTime": 77.7298903066,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんに頼られて喜ぶところが\n渚ちゃんらしいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being happy to be relied on by Kotono-chan…\nthat's so like you‚ Nagisa-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9165570496,
      "endTime": 82.4702759026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "そう言えば、渚がお姉ちゃんと会ったのも\nその頃だったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of which‚ that's around the time you met my sister‚ Nagisa.\nその頃だったわね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.663609131,
      "endTime": 87.1683525163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！\n渚ちゃんは麻奈さんに会ったことがあるんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?!\nYou met Mana-san‚ Nagisa-chan?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.3550192116,
      "endTime": 91.7338628052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "下校途中に声を掛けられてね……\nあの時はいきなりでびっくりしたなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She called out to me on my way home from school…\nIt was so sudden‚ I was surprised.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.9205295005,
      "endTime": 98.3953141607,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13479.470499599998,
          "startTime": 105.4000000001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_night",
      "startTime": 99.6319808083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、渚。また明日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See you tomorrow then‚ Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.6819808083,
      "endTime": 103.8515272217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "じゃーね、また明日！\nはぁ……今日も琴乃ちゃん可愛かったなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See you tomorrow!\nSigh… Kotono-chan was so cute again today~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.0448605932,
      "endTime": 113.10304693350001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9331.519730799997,
          "startTime": 113.376380324
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-03.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0430434302,
      "endTime": 116.5230403975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "え？　……えええええっ！\nな、長瀬麻奈さん！？　ほ、本物？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? …Whaaaat?!\nN-Nagase Mana-san?! I-is it really you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.7097070451,
      "endTime": 125.6510444398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mananame-02.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬麻奈です、はじめまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm Mana Nagase‚ nice to meet you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8643776968,
      "endTime": 129.4843548609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-03.m4a",
      "text": "あなた、伊吹渚ちゃんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're Nagisa Ibuki‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.6976881418,
      "endTime": 131.9243508336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-04.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃がいつも話してるから一目で分かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono talks about you all the time‚ so I knew it was you right away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.9243508336,
      "endTime": 135.8576868445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんが私のことを！？　嬉しい！\nって、そうじゃなくて、麻奈さんがどうしてここに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan talks about me?! I'm so happy!\nWait‚ that's not the point‚ why are you here‚ Mana-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.0643532823,
      "endTime": 146.5854426454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-09.m4a",
      "text": "駅から歩いて帰る途中、偶然琴乃と渚ちゃんを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was walking home from the station‚ and I happened to see Kotono and you‚ Nagisa-chan‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.7721091977,
      "endTime": 150.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-12.m4a",
      "text": "見かけたから、こっそり後をつけてたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I secretly followed you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.5333333333,
      "endTime": 153.838796114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "だったら声を掛けてくれれば良かったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then you should have just called out to us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.0387962094,
      "endTime": 158.1616307011,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-02.m4a",
      "text": "それが……今、ちょっと琴乃といろいろあって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… Kotono and I are going through a bit of a rough patch right now…",
