      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-04.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだ！　渚ちゃんを私のライブに招待するから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I know! I'll invite you to my live‚ Nagisa-chan‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 309.6095667902,
      "endTime": 313.4429158912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "琴乃を連れて一緒に観に来てくれないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "will you come with Kotono?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 313.4429158912,
      "endTime": 317.76662953600004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-02.m4a",
      "text": "ライブを観れば、琴乃もきっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If she sees my live‚ I'm sure",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 318.1429326756,
      "endTime": 320.7362335258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私の想いを分かってくれると思うから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono will understand how I feel.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 320.7362335258,
      "endTime": 323.9162336095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "でも、琴乃ちゃんはライブに誘っても\n行きたくないって言ってるんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Kotono-chan says she doesn't want to go\nto your lives.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 324.1095667902,
      "endTime": 330.9041451516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんが嫌がってるのなら\n無理強いはしたくありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Kotono-chan doesn't want to go‚\nI don't want to force her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 331.1041450563,
      "endTime": 336.20769100800004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs022.m4a",
      "text": "……だけど、もしも琴乃ちゃんが\n麻奈さんと仲直りしたいって言ったら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But if Kotono-chan\nsays she wants to make up with you‚ Mana-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 336.4943332892,
      "endTime": 342.72662193589997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs023.m4a",
      "text": "その時は、麻奈さんのライブに誘います\nそうすることが琴乃ちゃんのためだと思うから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "then I'll invite her to your live.\nBecause I think that's what's best for her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 342.9332883737,
      "endTime": 350.8332636507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_thanks-04.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、今はそれで十分だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ that's enough for now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 351.1598231854,
      "endTime": 356.3931851028,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "二人がライブに来てくれるのを待ってるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll be waiting for you both to come to my live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 356.3931851028,
      "endTime": 361.19994048999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……渚ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Nagisa-chan‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 361.6265325767,
      "endTime": 364.3598450564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-12.m4a",
      "text": "これからもずっと、琴乃の味方でいてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "please stay by Kotono's side.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 364.3598450564,
      "endTime": 369.1864960891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs024.m4a",
      "text": "はい。約束します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I promise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 369.3931626223,
      "endTime": 372.5665217074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
